Sometimes intense feelings of anger, sadness, fear, and shame threaten to take me under. The problems around me seem so huge and I feel so inadequate to change the world. It is at that point, where I accept that I did not create the world and do not hold the responsibility to shape it.  I can only be true to my destiny and that is enough.  Each one gets unique opportunities to have an impact.

